%3D0&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ff0d873f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581168-20210317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a6b86d75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581168-20210317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"強烈要求所有香港特區政府紀律部隊成員、所有疫苗專家委員會成員、所有特區政府公務員、所有駐港國安署成員、及其在港家屬，立即強制接種科興疫苗，即使已接種復必泰都要補加科興，以確保所有政府專業人員得到科興疫苗的最佳防護，有利於香港繁榮穩定！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4f960357dd173b8a051b655e5b9f122a3dab26","tid":2450721,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a56946676a56d406f1fa3b9ab6ad0a3d6187673","tid":2450721,"uid":166785,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"叫三萬隻popo打科興就有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"仲有佢哋家屬呀！"},{"pid":"c0f4a78f487fcca16874fe85436fcd8ca0b78c74","tid":2450721,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"其實依家班支那廢老同藍屍都開始試支那藥<br />\n唔使再昆佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943805f212e0a819d21ca9987806ac03731448b1","tid":2450721,"uid":92661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"咁科興有咩數據支持，拿出證據來。"},{"pid":"68f2b45951b2013f0715f6173d9b30e95ded338e","tid":2450721,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"你不如話死左果d收左錢唱衰科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6488d69f4469e87493e973b207a516da684956","tid":2450721,"uid":245886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"咁科興係唔夠數據 咁講有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠數據就刊登左醫學期刊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe8415bb4531f04b0969012c2a3112cf5ff3c39","tid":2450721,"uid":390224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"&lt;又中&gt; 東院護士接種科興疫苗 出現嚴重副作用留院 幾乎無法步行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2449751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2449751</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n藍營手足已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}